{"tid":592334,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"各位動物台手足入黎分享下自己既故事","createTime":"2018-03-14T06:31:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T09:51:25.000Z","uid":31374,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"98e7e0087d91683101f7bb7737028b9b097b02a1","tid":592334,"uid":31374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T06:31:24.000Z","msg":"講下我先<br />\n我中學果時都算多人追，雖然少少內向，但一D都稱唔上毒<br />\n咁中五果時膽粗粗去左同學長表白<br />\n佢拒絕我不特止，仲同班FD一齊笑我<br />\n我果陣自信心即刻趺到落谷底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n暴飲暴食又試過，兩三日唔番屋企又試過<br />\n係呢個時候，我其中一隻毒撚兵叫我試下睇刀劍神域<br />\n話咩會成為我既桐人喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經無咩求生意志既我就試下睇呢D公仔片，點知愈睇愈投入<br />\n睇到牙直話佢失戀果陣我喊左成晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後我就決定要同牙直一樣咁堅強，唔好衰俾人睇！<br />\n自此睇動漫亦都成為左我既興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然事後隻兵比我BLOCK左，但都好多謝佢令我振作起黎。"},{"pid":"303a4f271d3a397b413b754f9cdca71c12f2ff97","tid":592334,"uid":14719,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T06:33:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/14/143353_523271e245e1ab82564b28dab5558136.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F14%2F143353_523271e245e1ab82564b28dab5558136.png&h=dae0a991&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1fa484cebfff744cb5707b46377ed723d3803cda","tid":592334,"uid":1678,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T06:35:15.000Z","msg":"卡通就卡通啦 動咩漫"},{"pid":"1fa733837ef8e7dc79b30dff268734b472360780","tid":592334,"uid":31374,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1fa484cebfff744cb5707b46377ed723d3803cda","tid":592334,"uid":1678,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T06:35:15.000Z","msg":"卡通就卡通啦 動咩漫"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T06:41:13.000Z","msg":"卡通（火影，onepiece之類)係比細蚊仔睇<br />\n動漫（刀劍，SG之類）係比青少年以上既人睇"},{"pid":"a